 &lt;a class=&#34;footnote-return&#34; href=&#34;#fnref:11200-1&#34;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;[return]&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li id=&#34;fn:11200-2&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://sethgodin.typepad.com/seths_blog/2013/05/how-to-write-copy-that-goes-viral.html&#34;&gt;How to write copy that goes viral&lt;/a&gt;
